ng","size":"75","effect":"none","newTab":"false","linkUrl":"","variant":"logo","alignment":"left","borderColor":"#c5a059","borderRadius":"18","mobileHidden":"false","desktopHidden":"false","verticalMargin":"0","verticalOffset":"0","borderThickness":"2","horizontalOffset":"0"}}],"alignment":"left","canonical":true,"isPrivate":false,"marginTop":"0","background":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""},"cellHAlign":{"left":"left","right":"center","center":"left"},"cellShadow":{"left":"none","right":"none","center":"none"},"cellVAlign":{"left":"top","right":"top","center":"center"},"cellOpacity":{"left":"1","right":"1","center":"1"},"cellPadding":{"left":"0","right":"0","center":"0"},"marginBottom":"20","mobileHidden":"false","mobileLayout":"stack","cellIsPrivate":{"left":"false","right":"false","center":"false"},"desktopHidden":"false","overlayScreen":{"opacity":100,"background":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""}},"rowBorderColor":"#ffffff","rowBorderStyle":"solid","rowBorderWidth":"0","savedSectionId":"saved_section_1781826409772_rcsh6r","cellBackgrounds":{"left":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""},"right":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""},"center":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""}},"cellBorderColor":{"left":"#d9e4ef","right":"#999999","center":"#ffffff"},"cellBorderStyle":{"left":"solid","right":"solid","center":"solid"},"cellBorderWidth":{"left":"0","right":"0","center":"0"},"rowBorderRadius":"0","cellBorderRadius":{"left":"0","right":"14","center":"20"},"cellMobileHidden":{"left":"false","right":"false","center":"false"},"cellDesktopHidden":{"left":"false","right":"false","center":"false"},"cellVerticalMargin":{"left":"0","right":"0","center":"0"}},{"id":"348037cd-5139-48ea-86f2-3a03d32d4242","title":"Content Block 1","layout":"two-column","locked":false,"modules":[{"id":"module-ae640e95-5fca-45de-aaea-7ba97866a0d2","name":"","text":"<h1>Client Testimonials</h1><h2>Real Stories. Real Results. Real People We Were Honored to Help.</h2><p>At <strong>Marinoff &amp; Associates, P.C.</strong>, we are grateful for the trust our clients place in our firm during some of the most difficult moments of their lives. Whether facing criminal charges, immigration challenges, traffic matters, or life-changing legal situations, our clients deserve strong advocacy, honest guidance, and personal attention.</p><p>Below are testimonials from individuals and families who have worked with Brandon Marinoff and the team at Marinoff &amp; Associates.</p><h2>Featured Testimonials</h2><blockquote><p>“I was facing life. I was innocent. Brandon saved my life, and now I am a free man. Thank you!”<br><strong>— Jaime, Greeley, CO</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“My entire life was on the line. A complete nightmare had taken over my life. I had been sitting in jail for months on a very serious felony. But I was innocent. I knew it in my heart, but no other attorney believed me or gave me a chance. My family met with Brandon Marinoff and was impressed with his fighting spirit and brutal honesty. When a person is in my type of situation, the last thing they need is to be lied to, and Brandon was the most honest man I had ever met. Brandon Marinoff was fair and gave us a reasonable deal for my case. We went to a jury trial that lasted three days. The jury found me not guilty within one hour after the trial ended. I owe my life to Brandon Marinoff.”<br><strong>— Client</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“This letter is made with a lot of gratitude for you and the entire staff at your office. I thank God that He guided you to do a good job for my son, Sergio Castillo, who was in prison for seven years. When a son is incarcerated, the whole family is also incarcerated, but thanks to you we see the light. We will always be grateful to you, and we will keep you in our prayers. God bless you and your staff too.”<br><strong>— A Client Family, Denver, CO</strong></p></blockquote><h1>Criminal Defense Testimonials</h1><blockquote><p>“Mr. Marinoff has represented me in multiple cases over the years and has always delivered excellent results beyond expectation. He is extremely personable, professional, and attentive. By far the best legal representation available.”<br><strong>— Justin</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“Excellent Outcome! Brandon and his office staff were professional and diligent in keeping us informed of case status. We lived out of state, and he was willing to work with the court to allow for the least amount of travel and expense possible. We appreciate the help during a difficult time and were able to get a positive outcome, thus not impacting the rest of our lives. Thank you!”<br><strong>— Client</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“Honesty. Brandon and his staff are very welcoming, which is a must when you are in problems and looking for help. Not only are they welcoming and make you feel like family, but they are professional. Brandon has a lot of knowledge about cases and is very upfront and honest. Every time I ever need legal advice, I will come to Brandon and his team.”<br><strong>— Guillermo</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“Excellent Attorney. I highly recommend Marinoff and Associates!”<br><strong>— A Former Client</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“Marinoff is honest! Brandon Marinoff has worked with me several times. He is a great criminal defense attorney, he is honest, and he is very intelligent. From the first day we stepped into his office, his staff and his other lawyer were friendly. Brandon won’t take your case if he absolutely knows he can’t do anything for you. In other words, he won’t promise you a miracle just to take your money. He got me an awesome deal. I will forever thank him!”<br><strong>— Javier</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“Great Job! I hit a really bad stretch in my life, and I picked up two DUI charges within one year of each other. I was looking at serving one year in jail and losing my job that I had just been promoted to. I hired the Law Office of Brandon Marinoff to help me with my cases. They did a great job, and I received a much better outcome than I expected. Thank you, Brandon Marinoff.”<br><strong>— Angelica</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“This lawyer has been one of the few who are honest when they really can’t do anything about your case, instead of saying they can and taking your money. I appreciate his honesty. He has helped my cousin in a drug case, and it turned out great. I will continue to go here and send more people his way.”<br><strong>— Client</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“I have worked with Brandon and his team professionally and have witnessed his ferocious defense of his clients in their cases. I would recommend him highly for those seeking a competent and aggressive defense attorney.”<br><strong>— Dr. David</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“With their help, I have one more shot at keeping my driver’s license. They reduced my large ticket to manageable points and fines. I would most definitely hire them again, as well as refer them to friends. I drive a lot, and the thought of losing my license was unbearable. What they did for me by lowering my points was beyond words.”<br><strong>— R.L., Lakewood, CO</strong></p></blockquote><h1>Immigration Testimonials</h1><blockquote><p>“Ruben hired Brandon Marinoff and his services, and he treated me very well and with care. He helped me fix my legal status in this country, and I am very happy with the job he did. I thank him for all the help and work he did for me, and I know he will keep helping everyone he can.”<br><strong>— Ruben, Longmont, CO</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“The overall service from Marinoff &amp; Associates has been excellent for the way he has treated and helped me. I have known him for two years, and I appreciate his good service. I will be back if I need further help and assistance. On top of everything, he and his staff are very respectful and prestigious people.”<br><strong>— Juan A., Cheyenne, WY</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“I would recommend Brandon Marinoff and his staff highly. I had my case, and it went very well. My case was resolved without any complications. I highly recommend them.”<br><strong>— Raul and Maria Elena, Thornton, CO</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“Fantastic immigration service. Brandon and his team have helped my family and friends, and my husband now has his permanent residency in this country. Thank you, Brandon! I will definitely recommend him to anyone who needs an honest attorney for immigration or criminal problems.”<br><strong>— Laura and Jose</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“Brandon Marinoff is an amazing attorney! I would recommend this law firm to anyone in need of a good immigration lawyer, or if you need an attorney for criminal cases. They are honest and care about their clients. Thank you, Brandon, and your team for all the hard work you put into our case. We greatly appreciate it. No words will ever amount to how grateful we are.”<br><strong>— Erica</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“Thank you Brandon Marinoff and to all your associates for all the hard work you put into our case! We are forever grateful for everything you have done for us.”<br><strong>— Erica</strong></p></blockquote><h1>Client Experience Testimonials</h1><blockquote><p>“I am so grateful for all of the help I received during my case. Someone was always available to answer my questions. What a great guy—warm, caring, competent. A breath of fresh air! I would highly recommend anyone utilize their expertise.”<br><strong>— Sarah, Tennis Professional</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“I absolutely love this firm and their team. They actually take the time to get to know their clients and help with your case instead of other firms who only care about the money they can rake in. Very professional and very helpful. Highly recommended.”<br><strong>— Dakota</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“Anyone in the Westminster area, look no further. Brandon and his team have helped myself and multiple friends dramatically, whether it was from a DUI or when I decided to race a cop and run.”<br><strong>— Quinlan</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“Mr. Marinoff and his entire staff are an exceptional team. They are professional and work hard to defend your rights. I highly recommend them for all your legal needs.”<br><strong>— Monica</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“Very loyal, does a lot of research, and always wins his cases. Very professional, and I would highly recommend him.”<br><strong>— Chavela</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>“Really good lawyer. Definitely recommend him. Nice and polite.”<br><strong>— Olga</strong></p></blockquote><h1>Trusted Legal Guidance When It Matters Most</h1><p>At Marinoff &amp; Associates, P.C., every case matters because every client matters. We are proud to serve individuals and families throughout Colorado in criminal defense and immigration law matters.</p><p><strong>Your Rights. Your Family. Your Future. Our Commitment.</strong></p><p>Contact Marinoff &amp; Associates today to schedule a consultation and learn how our experienced legal team can help.</p><p><em>Testimonials reflect individual client experiences. Prior results do not guarantee a similar outcome in future cases.</em></p>","type":"text","column":"left","settings":{"variant":"intro","mobileHidden":"false","desktopHidden":"false","verticalMargin":"0"}},{"id":"86aa7632-5560-46ab-b6f7-d401d6ff04a3","name":"Justice","text":"","type":"image","column":"right","settings":{"al