time. While Marinoff &amp; Associates, P.C. strives to provide accurate and helpful information, we do not guarantee that all information on this website is current, complete, or applicable to your particular circumstances.</p><p>You should consult with an attorney to receive advice based on the current law and the specific facts of your case.</p><h2>Third-Party Links</h2><p>This website may include links to third-party websites for convenience or informational purposes. Marinoff &amp; Associates, P.C. does not control and is not responsible for the content, accuracy, security, or privacy practices of any third-party websites.</p><h2>Contacting the Firm</h2><p>If you need legal advice regarding a criminal defense or immigration matter, please contact Marinoff &amp; Associates, P.C. directly to schedule a consultation.</p><p><strong>Marinoff &amp; Associates, P.C.</strong><br><strong>Westminster:</strong> 10455 Sheridan Blvd., Suite 210, Westminster, CO 80020<br><strong>Brighton:</strong> 150 South 4th Avenue, Suite 200, Brighton, CO 80601<br><strong>Greeley:</strong> 609 8th Street, Suite 200, Greeley, CO 80631</p><p><strong>Phone:</strong> 720-373-3508<br><strong>Additional Phone:</strong> 720-216-4766<br><strong>Website:</strong> <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"http://www.brandonmarinoff.com\">www.brandonmarinoff.com</a></p><p><strong>Se Habla Español</strong></p><p><em>This disclaimer is provided for general website use and should be reviewed by legal counsel to ensure compliance with all applicable rules, regulations, and professional responsibility requirements.</em></p>","type":"text","column":"left","settings":{"variant":"intro","mobileHidden":"false","desktopHidden":"false","verticalMargin":"0"}},{"id":"86aa7632-5560-46ab-b6f7-d401d6ff04a3","name":"Justice","text":"","type":"image","column":"right","settings":{"alt":"Justice","url":"https://astujhe2hvjqd0kf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/APP_Assets/Image/1782579267114_Personal_Immigra