"},"cellVerticalMargin":{"left":"0","right":"0","center":"0"}},{"id":"section-100dbb11-5fc4-4bb8-a328-c4ab72d52dd5","title":"Welcome to Marinoff & Associates","layout":"two-column","locked":false,"modules":[{"id":"module-6aea8635-5986-4932-ad4d-220cf073855c","name":"","text":"<h1>Welcome to Marinoff &amp; Associates</h1><h3>Experienced Representation. Personalized Attention. Results That Matter.</h3><p>At <strong>Marinoff &amp; Associates, P.C.</strong>, we understand that legal problems are rarely just legal problems. They often involve your freedom, your family, your reputation, your immigration status, and your future. Whether you are facing criminal charges, navigating a family dispute, or pursuing an immigration matter, you deserve experienced legal guidance and an advocate who genuinely cares about your outcome.</p><p><strong>With offices conveniently located in Westminster, Brighton, and Greeley, we proudly represent clients throughout Colorado in Criminal Law and Immigration Law matters.</strong> Our team is committed to providing skilled legal representation with compassion, integrity, and unwavering dedication.</p><p>At <strong>Marinoff &amp; Associates, P.C.</strong>, we proudly represent individuals and families throughout Colorado with experienced, compassionate, and results-driven legal counsel. Whether you are facing criminal charges or pursuing your immigration goals, our attorneys are committed to providing personalized guidance and aggressive advocacy every step of the way.</p>","type":"text","column":"left","settings":{"variant":"paragraph","mobileHidden":"false","desktopHidden":"false","verticalMargin":"0"}},{"id":"module-868b31c0-b69e-4e42-896d-afdd646267a0","name":"","text":"","type":"image","column":"right","settings":{"alt":"Criminal Defense and Immigration Attorneys","url":"https://astujhe2hvjqd0kf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/APP_Assets/Image/Stock_Photos/1782945687006_One_Moment_960x960.jpg","size":"90","effect":"none","newTab":"false","linkUrl":"","variant":"image","alignment":"center","borderColor":"#0f4f8f","borderRadius":"18","mobileHidden":"false","desktopHidden":"false","verticalMargin":"0","verticalOffset":"0","borderThickness":"0","horizontalOffset":"0"}}],"alignment":"left","isPrivate":false,"marginTop":"0","background":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""},"cellHAlign":{"left":"left","right":"left"},"cellShadow":{"left":"none","right":"none"},"cellVAlign":{"left":"top","right":"top"},"cellOpacity":{"left":"1","right":"1"},"cellPadding":{"left":"18","right":"18"},"marginBottom":"0","mobileHidden":"false","mobileLayout":"stack","cellIsPrivate":{"left":"false","right":"false"},"desktopHidden":"false","overlayScreen":{"opacity":100,"background":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""}},"rowBorderColor":"#000000","rowBorderStyle":"solid","rowBorderWidth":"0","cellBackgrounds":{"left":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""},"right":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""}},"cellBorderColor":{"left":"transparent","right":"transparent"},"cellBorderStyle":{"left":"solid","right":"solid"},"cellBorderWidth":{"left":"0","right":"0"},"rowBorderRadius":"0","cellBorderRadius":{"left":"24","right":"24"},"cellMobileHidden":{"left":"false","right":"false"},"cellDesktopHidden":{"left":"false","right":"false"},"cellVerticalMargin":{"left":"0","right":"0"}},{"id":"a1e625d9-8275-4de6-b781-4860fe797944","title":"What Makes Our Firm Different?","layout":"two-column","locked":false,"modules":[{"id":"21980bd3-e205-445e-a49f-cc96ea09ac78","name":"","text":"<h2>What Makes Our Firm Different?</h2><p>Many law firms handle cases.</p><p>We build relationships.</p><p>We understand that legal issues affect every part of a person''s life—from family and employment to finances and peace of mind.</p><p>That is why we combine legal experience with personalized attention, clear communication, and genuine compassion.</p><p>Our clients know they have someone in their corner who will fight tirelessly for their interests while treating them with dignity and respect.</p><p><strong>Your case is important. Your future matters. And we are here to help.</strong></p>","type":"text","column":"right","settings":{"variant":"paragraph","mobileHidden":"false","desktopHidden":"false","verticalMargin":"0"}},{"id":"fa53b1a0-9420-4236-9c73-2272fa4c696a","name":"","text":"","type":"image","column":"left","settings":{"alt":"Criminal Defense Attorney - Westminster CO","url":"https://astujhe2hvjqd0kf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/APP_Assets/Image/1782844578210_Criminal_Defense_Attorney_-_Westminster_CO.png","size":"90","effect":"none","newTab":"false","linkUrl":"","variant":"image","borderColor":"#0f4f8f","borderRadius":"18","mobileHidden":"false","desktopHidden":"false","verticalMargin":"0","verticalOffset":"0","borderThickness":"0","horizontalOffset":"0"}}],"alignment":"left","isPrivate":false,"marginTop":"0","background":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""},"cellHAlign":{"left":"left","right":"left"},"cellShadow":{"left":"none","right":"none"},"cellVAlign":{"left":"top","right":"top"},"cellOpacity":{"left":"1","right":"1"},"cellPadding":{"left":"18","right":"18"},"marginBottom":"0","mobileHidden":"false","mobileLayout":"stack","cellIsPrivate":{"left":"false","right":"false"},"desktopHidden":"false","overlayScreen":{"opacity":100,"background":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""}},"rowBorderColor":"#000000","rowBorderStyle":"solid","rowBorderWidth":"0","cellBackgrounds":{"left":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""},"right":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""}},"cellBorderColor":{"left":"transparent","right":"transparent"},"cellBorderStyle":{"left":"solid","right":"solid"},"cellBorderWidth":{"left":"0","right":"0"},"rowBorderRadius":"0","cellBorderRadius":{"left":"24","right":"24"},"cellMobileHidden":{"left":"false","right":"false"},"cellDesktopHidden":{"left":"false","right":"false"},"cellVerticalMargin":{"left":"0","right":"0"}},{"id":"53c1db1b-0ddc-443a-9150-d77fa7c12c1d","title":"Protecting Your Rights, Family, and Future","layout":"two-column","locked":false,"modules":[{"id":"537fb4ed-7803-4a05-b319-b2224268300e","name":"","text":"<h2>Protecting Your Rights, Family, and Future</h2><h3><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://brandonmarinoff.com/criminal-law/\">Criminal Law</a></h3><p>When your rights and freedom are on the line, experience matters. We provide strategic defense for misdemeanors, felonies, DUI cases, traffic offenses, drug crimes, theft, fraud, violent crimes, and other criminal charges. We work diligently to protect your rights, challenge the evidence, and pursue the strongest possible outcome.</p><h3><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://brandonmarinoff.com/immigration-law/\">Immigration Law</a></h3><p>Navigating the immigration system can be overwhelming, but you do not have to face it alone. We assist individuals and families with visas, green cards, citizenship, family-based immigration, student visas, and other immigration matters, providing clear guidance and experienced representation every step of the way.</p><p></p>","type":"text","column":"left","settings":{"variant":"paragraph","mobileHidden":"false","desktopHidden":"false","verticalMargin":"0"}},{"id":"16611494-81b0-40a8-88f7-28e57745bece","name":"","text":"","type":"image","column":"right","settings":{"alt":"Personal Attention by Lawyers","url":"https://astujhe2hvjqd0kf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/APP_Assets/Image/1781877100941_Legal_Problems.png","size":"90","effect":"none","newTab":"false","linkUrl":"","variant":"image","alignment":"center","borderColor":"#0f4f8f","borderRadius":"18","mobileHidden":"false","desktopHidden":"false","verticalMargin":"0","verticalOffset":"0","borderThickness":"0","horizontalOffset":"0"}}],"alignment":"left","isPrivate":false,"marginTop":"0","background":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""},"cellHAlign":{"left":"left","right":"left"},"cellShadow":{"left":"none","right":"none"},"cellVAlign":{"left":"top","right":"top"},"cellOpacity":{"left":"1","right":"1"},"cellPadding":{"left":"18","right":"18"},"marginBottom":"0","mobileHidden":"false","mobileLayout":"stack","cellIsPrivate":{"left":"false","right":"false"},"desktopHidden":"false","overlayScreen":{"opacity":100,"background":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""}},"rowBorderColor":"#000000","rowBorderStyle":"solid","rowBorderWidth":"0","cellBackgrounds":{"left":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""},"right":{"mode":"none","color":"#ffffff","color2":"#eaf4ff","opacity":100,"imageUrl":"","styleKey":"","imageAssetId":""}},"cellBorderColor":{"left":"transparent","right":"transparent"},"cellBorderStyle":{"left":"solid","right":"solid"},"cellBorderWidth":{"left":"0","right":"0"},"rowBorderRadius":"0","cellBorderRadius":{"left":"24","right":"24"},"cellMobileHidden":{"left":"false","right":"false"},"cellDesktopHidden":{"left":"false","right":"false"},"cellVerticalMargin":{"left":"0","right":"0"}},{"id":"5aa66254-e76d-414c-b113-1daf35fef115","title":"Why Clients Choose Marinoff & Associates","layout":"two-column","locked":false,"modules":[{"id":"c40420f5-a734-4157-8b4a-7186fc0c93e4","name":"","text":"","type":"image","column":"left","settings":{"alt":"Colorado Immigration Lawyers","url":"https://astujhe2hvjqd0kf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/APP_Assets/Image/1782844675677_Best_Criminal_Lawyer_Brandon_Marinoff.png","size":"100","effect":"none","newTab":"false","linkUrl":"","variant":"image","borderColor":"#0f4f8f","borderRadius":"18","mobileHidden":"false","desktopHidden":"false","verticalMargin":"35","verticalOffset":"0","borderThickness":"0","horizontalOffset":"0"}},{"id":"8d6c9665-9901-4680-9f40-b02eb8febecc","name":"","text":"<h2>Why Clients Choose Marinoff &amp; Associates</h2><p><strong>Experienced Attorneys</strong><br>Our team brings years of legal experience and a deep understanding of Colorado''s criminal, family, and immigration laws.</p><p><strong>Personalized Representation</strong><br>Every case is different. We take the time to understand your circumstances, listen to your concerns, and develop legal strategies tailored to your specific needs.</p><p><strong>Committed to Results</strong><br>We are dedicated to protecting your rights and pursuing the best possible outcome, no matter how complex your situation may be.</p><p><strong>Accessible and Responsive</strong><br>With offices in Westminster, Brighton, and Greeley, we are proud to serve clients throughout Colorado and provide responsive, client-focused representation.</p><p>At Marinoff &amp; Associates, your case is our priority because your future matters. We are here to help you understand your options, protect your rights, and guide you through life''s most difficult legal challenges.</p><p><strong>Your Rights. Your Family. Your Future. Our Commitment.</strong></p><p>Call us today at <strong>720-373-3508 (Se Habla Español)</strong> or <strong>720-216-4766</strong> to schedule a consultation and discuss your unique situation.</p>","type":"text","column":"right","settings":{"variant":"paragraph","mobileHidden":"false","desktopHidden":"false","verticalMargin":"0"}},{"id":"module-9bbbb667-a5ba-489f-8e91-58b0900f908c"